<div class="addon-config">
    <h2>Zablu API</h2>
    <p>Configure as credenciais da API do Zablu abaixo:</p>
    
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="api_url">URL da API:</label>
        <input type="text" name="api_url" value="{$api_url}" size="100" class="form-control">
        <p class="help-block">URL base da API do Zablu (ex: https://api.zablu.com.br)</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="api_key">Chave da API:</label>
        <input type="password" name="api_key" value="{$api_key}" size="100" class="form-control">
        <p class="help-block">Chave de acesso da API do Zablu</p>
    </div>
</div>
